About

Eating in        Italian

Salumeria Rosi is an Italian restaurant, salumi & delicatessen shop, bringing the best of Northern Italy to the Upper West Side, NYC since 2008. Shop imported meats and cheeses, enjoy handcrafted pasta, classic Italian wine and cocktails along with thoughtful hospitality, creating a warm and exciting dining experience. With inviting outdoor seating and a warm interior, our space is perfect for everything from a quick breakfast to an elegant lunch, a relaxed dinner, or a leisurely weekend brunch.

An Italian Restaurant, Deli, Salumeria, Meat and Cheese Store on the Upper West Side, New York City, offering gluten-free and vegetarian dishes, Italian catering, Italian takeout and food delivery. Join us for lunch, dinner, and brunch. Outdoor and indoor dining available. Salumeria Rosi is conveniently located near Lincoln Center, Beacon Theatre & The Metropolitan Opera.
